wedding with you.

314
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:16,590
Don't worry about Jake—
I'll get him there
in plenty of time.

315
00:14:16,660 --> 00:14:18,100
Well, you are
very welcome.

316
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:20,560
Best of luck to you
and her. Bye-bye.

317
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:22,440
I'm going to the wedding.

318
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,830
♪ Men... ♪

319
00:14:27,900 --> 00:14:29,570
What is this, candle wax?

320
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:33,710
How do you get candle wax
on the seat of your pants?

321
00:14:33,780 --> 00:14:35,650
I don't know.
You don't know?

322
00:14:35,710 --> 00:14:38,710
Okay, I might've lit
a couple of farts.

323
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:44,360
I'm ready. Myra's ready.
Is he ready?

324
00:14:44,420 --> 00:14:45,480
Does he look ready?

325
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:47,620
Well,

326
00:14:47,690 --> 00:14:49,760
