333
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,560
You know what?

334
00:15:26,630 --> 00:15:27,870
I just realized something.

335
00:15:27,930 --> 00:15:31,740
I am two for two
at Judith's weddings.

336
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:35,870
What a coincidence—
I'm two for two
at Herb's weddings.

337
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:37,810
Oh. Okay.

338
00:15:37,870 --> 00:15:39,300
