390
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:53,370
Nice dress.

391
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:54,670
Bite me.

392
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:57,470
Okay. Meet me
in the coatroom.
(laughs)

393
00:17:57,550 --> 00:18:00,690
Listen, after the reception,
can you take me to the airport?

394
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:02,360
You're flying
home tonight?

395
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:03,590
Yeah.

396
00:18:03,650 --> 00:18:05,320
I thought we had
something going here.

397
00:18:05,390 --> 00:18:06,860
We did, and now
I'm going home.

398
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:09,350
Okay. Maybe I can come
visit you sometime.

399
00:18:09,430 --> 00:18:11,830
Ooh, I don't think my boyfriend
would like that very much.

400
00:18:11,890 --> 00:18:13,760
Your boyfriend?

401
00:18:13,830 --> 00:18:15,440
He's more like a fiancé.

402
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:16,870
You're getting married?

403
00:18:18,800 --> 00:18:21,430
(organ playing "Wedding March")

404
00:18:26,110 --> 00:18:28,650
(whispers):
Why didn't you tell me
you were engaged?

405
00:18:28,710 --> 00:18:30,510
