406
00:18:30,580 --> 00:18:31,790
(loudly):
Awkward?

407
00:18:45,390 --> 00:18:48,390
MINISTER:
You may be seated.

408
00:18:53,700 --> 00:18:56,500
Mm, ow. We-we really
shouldn't be doing this.

409
00:18:56,570 --> 00:18:58,370
Why not?
They broke our hearts.

410
00:18:58,440 --> 00:18:59,840
Uh, yeah, but I'm
kind of over it.

411
00:18:59,910 --> 00:19:01,410
I'm not.

412
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:04,520
Mm, mm, uh,
hang on, hang on.

413
00:19:04,580 --> 00:19:06,040
Maybe we could go out
for coffee first.

414
00:19:06,110 --> 00:19:07,710
