440
00:20:29,730 --> 00:20:32,430
(clears throat):
So...

441
00:20:32,500 --> 00:20:34,460
drinking in the dark, eh?

442
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:38,040
It wasn't dark
when I started.

443
00:20:38,110 --> 00:20:40,980
Did you get Myra
to the airport?

444
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:42,470
Yep.

445
00:20:42,540 --> 00:20:43,970
And you know what?

446
00:20:44,050 --> 00:20:45,590
I'll never see her again.

447
00:20:45,650 --> 00:20:48,120
I was just a meaningless fling
to that girl.

448
00:20:48,180 --> 00:20:50,810
